name: Miniscule
description: Becomes super small and raises evasion against attacks by 1 stage upon entering the battlefield.

name: Icky
description: Boosts the power of OOZE & FUNGAL type attacks by 20%.

name: Burdened
description: A large growth reduces SPD by 1 stage but raises DEF by 1 stage upon entering the battlefield.

name: Broodmother
description: Gains 1 stage of ATK for each Oochamon with the same type in the party.

name: Tough
description: A durable body grants a 1 stage increase to DEF upon entering the battlefield.

name: Shadow
description: Grants a 25% chance to VANISH after being attacked.

name: Withering
description: Withers away the opposing Oochamon, lowering it's DEF by 1 stage upon entering the battlefield.

name: Darkbright
description: Attacks that afflict BURN also BLIND and vice-versa.

name: Gentle
description: A kind heart reduces both your ATK and the enemy ATK by 1 stage.

name: Warm
description: Raises the damage of FLAME attacks by 10%.

name: Radiant
description: Dangerous energy causes attacks that BURN also INFECT.

name: Conflicted
description: Multiple minds increase ALL stats by 1 stage upon entering the battlefield.

name: Burrower
description: Raises the damage of STONE attacks by 10%.

name: Reactive
description: When hit by an attack, reflects 10% of the attacker's HP as damage.

name: Inertia
description: Raises SPD by 1 stage each turn.

name: Dense
description: Raises ATK by 1 stage but reduces SPD by 1 stage upon entering the battlefield.

name: Moist
description: Halves all incoming FLAME damage.

name: Alert
description: Raises ATK by 1 stage when an Oochamon switches in.

name: Fleeting
description: Raises SPD and ATK by 2 stages but also loses half of current HP each turn.

name: Efficient
description: Raises ATK by 1 stage every other turn.

name: Boisterous
description: Shatters eardrums when it enters the field dealing 10% of the enemy's HP.

name: Haunted
description: Applies the DOOMED status to an enemy when the Haunted Oochamon faints.

name: Leech
description: Restores HP equal to 10% of damage done to the enemy.

name: Ensnare
description: Grants a 30% chance to SNARE an enemy when attacking.

name: Uncontrolled
description: Raises ATK by 3 stages and reduces DEF by 1 stages upon entering the battlefield, but randomly chooses an attack each turn.

name: Apprentice
description: Raises ATK by 2 stages if any other party members share a move with it.

name: Focused
description: Raises damage of attacks by 10% if unaffected by status effects.

name: Ravenous
description: Restores 20% of max HP upon defeating an enemy.

name: Immense
description: Raises DEF by 2 stages upon entering the battlefield, but also makes opponent's moves always hit.

name: Armored
description: Reduces STONE damage by 20%.

name: Scorching
description: Attacks that can BURN always BURN.

name: Tangled
description: Causes enemies that hit it to be SNARED.

name: Mundane
description: Makes the Oochamon completely immune to Status Effects.

name: Rogue
description: Doubles the damage dealt to full HP enemies.

name: Crystallize
description: Boosts the power of Ooze, Flame, and Crystal attacks by 30%.

name: Lacerating
description: All attacks do an extra attack to an enemy, dealing 5% of their max HP.

name: Gravity
description: Attacks deal 1% more damage per number of turns in this battle.

name: Sporespray
description: INFECTS the enemy when the Sporespray Oochamon faints.

name: Frostbite
description: Attacks that strike an enemy reduce their SPD by 1 stage.

name: Bipolar
description: Use the DEF stat when dealing damage, rather than the ATK stat.

name: Hexiply
description: Attacks deal 6% more damage per sixth of HP remaining.

name: Nullify
description: Nullify's the opposing Oochamon, changing their ability to Null while out on the field.

name: Duplicant
description: Copies the opponent's ability.

name: Null
description: Does nothing.

name: Immobile
description: Always go last when attacking, but gain a DEF increase upon entering the battlefield.

name: Strings Attached
description: Gains a 20% chance to apply a randomly apply BURN, INFECT, BLIND, or SNARE when attacking.

name: Corrosive
description: Attacks deal more damage to enemies with high DEF.

name: Spectral
description: Changes the Spectral Oochamon's type to Magic every other turn.

name: Height Advantage
description: Raises chance to do a critical hit by 10%.

name: Hearty
description: Raises damage done by 15% while above 50% HP.

name: Radioactive
description: Changes the Radioactive Oochamon's type to Flame every other turn.

name: Energized
description: Raises ATK and SPD by 1 stage on kill.

name: Patient
description: Raises DEF by 1 stage every other turn.

name: Easy Go
description: Heals the rest of the Oochamon Trainer's party by 20% of their max HP when defeated.

name: Bomber
description: The Oochamon explodes upon fainting, dealing half of the opposing Oochamon's HP on death.

name: Flammable
description: Gains 1 stage of ATK when hit with a FLAME type move.

name: Hole Dweller
description: Gets the Vanished status at the end of every other turn.

name: Power Conduit
description: Boosts the power of FLAME moves against OOZE and TECH types by 50%.

name: Liquid Cooled
description: Prevents BURN and boosts the power of TECH type moves by 25%.

name: Increment
description: Randomly boosts a stat by 1 stage at the end of each turn.

name: Parry
description: Reduces damage taken by 20%. When hit by an attack, this ability becomes Riposte.

name: Riposte
description: Raises damage dealt by 20%. After attacking or when the turn ends, this ability becomes Parry.

name: Swaying
description: Raises DEF by 1 stage upon entering the battlefield, but also lowers accuracy by 1 stage.

name: Thrashing
description: Raises ATK by 1 stage upon entering the battlefield, but also lowers evasion by 1 stage.

name: Union
description: Raises ATK and DEF by 1 stage.

name: Protector
description: The Oochamon gets protected, making it immune to moves it resists during the turn it switches in.

name: Phantasmal
description: The Oochamon is phantasmal, making it immune to Neutral-type moves.

name: Matryoshka
description: The first time the Oochamon would faint, revives and restores its HP to half.

name: Thorned
description: Attacks deal extra damage based on DEF.

name: Downward Spiral
description: Randomly lowers one of its stats 1 stage at the end of each turn.

name: Constructor
description: Raises DEF by 1 stage when hit by a Stone-type move.

name: Neutralizer
description: The special effects of damaging attacks are ignored, but their damage is increased by 30%.

name: Bass Boost
description: Boosts the power of Sound moves by 15%.

name: Stealthy
description: The Oochamon becomes stealthy, gaining the status effect **FOCUSED** if it hasn't dealt damage this turn.

name: Pursuer
description: Deals 20% current HP damage to an Oochamon as it switches out.

name: Bloodrush
description: Taking damage raises SPD by 1 stage.

name: Chronomancy
description: Damaging moves get -1 Priority. Other moves get +1 Priority.

name: Martyr
description: If this Oochamon is swapped out with 0 HP, Raises the ATK of the next mon to switch in.

name: Condiment
description: Raises the DEF & SPD of Lasangato in the party 1 stage.

name: Double or Nothing
description: Attacks damage is either doubled or reduced to 0.

name: Vigorous
description: Raises healing done by moves by 30%.

name: Turbine
description: Raises ATK whenever it uses a Flame-type attack.

name: Pact
description: Raises the damage of the user's first move by 30% on repeated uses.

name: Exploiter
description: The EXPOSED status triples damage instead of doubling it.

name: Seer
description: If the Oochamon would be EXPOSED it instead gains +1 SPD.

name: Escalation Protocol
description: Gets +1 ATK, DEF, & SPD per 20% HP lost.

name: Spreading Sludge
description: Spawns a helpful Slime Head per 20% HP lost.

name: Ancient Plating
description: Spawns a Ancient Rune per 20% HP lost.

name: Ancient Ward
description: Allied Oochamon take reduced damage for attacks that match this Oochamon's type.

name: Usurper
description: Queues the same attack after an enemy Oochamon attacks.

name: Pure Core
description: Reduces the damage of incoming non-Super Effective moves.
